you're obsessed with him.

00:06.173 --> 00:07.883
<i>You're saying</i>
<i>that I moved here from New York,</i>

00:07.966 --> 00:11.136
<i>and I left behind a job</i>
<i>that would have paid me $545,000 a year,</i>

00:11.220 --> 00:14.556
<i>for a guy I dated for two months</i>
<i>when I was 16 at a summer camp?</i>

00:14.640 --> 00:16.975
<i>Here's what happened.</i>
<i>I was in New York. I ran into Josh.</i>

00:17.059 --> 00:19.561
<i>He made me feel warm inside</i>
<i>like glitter was exploding inside me.</i>

00:19.645 --> 00:22.105
Then I moved here.
I did not move here because of Josh.

00:22.189 --> 00:24.566
Because that would be crazy
and I am not crazy.

00:24.650 --> 00:28.487
I'm so happy that you're in town,
and I don't think you're crazy at all.

00:28.570 --> 00:30.364
I love him so much.

00:30.447 --> 00:32.324
-Do you love her?
-No.

00:32.407 --> 00:35.702
