that ruins any possibility

00:40.374 --> 00:43.835
<i>for when you finally come to your senses</i>
<i>and realize that you are meant for Josh.</i>

00:43.919 --> 00:46.088
-You're sleeping with Rebecca?
-All the time, a lot.

00:46.171 --> 00:49.216
It's Greg? It's Greg?
You're sleeping with Greg?

00:49.299 --> 00:51.260
I care about you a lot.

00:51.343 --> 00:54.513
We have fun together,
but let's not, like, plan out our future.

00:54.596 --> 00:57.933
-Wait, what?
-[Josh] <i>Rebecca, Valencia and I are done.</i>

00:58.016 --> 01:01.270
Come with me.
No matter what I do, I feel you with me.

01:01.353 --> 01:04.648
Can I tell you something?
I moved here for you.

01:04.731 --> 01:06.900
<i>This is our moment, Josh Chan.</i>

01:06.984 --> 01:10.779
I'm so excited that our love story
can finally begin.

01:27.671 --> 01:29.298
Did you mean what you said?

01:31.133 --> 01:33.218
You moved here for me?

01:36.597 --> 01:37.681
Okay...

01:38.849 --> 01:40.434
Yes.

01:40.517 --> 01:41.935
Yes. Yes, I did.

01:42.019 --> 01:45.397
And I know it sounds weird,
but allow me-- Okay.

01:45.480 --> 01:48.650
You have to understand,
when I ran into you in New York,

01:48.734 --> 01:51.903
I was at a very low moment.

01:51.987 --> 01:55.574
And I mean, I don't know.
If I'd run into Reuben Fishwell...

01:55.657 --> 01:57.492
Remember that guy from camp
with the chapped lips?

01:57.576 --> 01:59.995
If I'd run into him... I don't know...

02:00.078 --> 02:03.790
I might have fallen into Michigan
and started a lip balm company.

02:04.666 --> 02:05.500
Okay.

02:05.584 --> 02:11.173
But what did you mean when you said,
"Our love story can finally begin"?

02:13.967 --> 02:17.304
Um, our what? Our-- Our love story?

02:17.387 --> 02:20.140
-I didn't say that. You said that.
-Wait, what?

02:20.223 --> 02:23.393
