and figure out why you're so fixated

02:23.477 --> 02:26.021
on every little thing I supposedly said.

02:26.104 --> 02:29.107
'Cause it feels like you're
an emotional stenographer right now.

02:29.191 --> 02:32.319
-You definitely said our--
-Okay. Let's recap the events of tonight.

02:32.402 --> 02:34.905
So, you show up at Jayma's wedding,
looking all Danny Zuko,

02:34.988 --> 02:37.908
and the leather jacket
that literally came out of space,

02:37.991 --> 02:39.785
clutching my old camp letter
to your heart, saying you can't stop thinking about me.

02:41.745 --> 02:43.705
-Right, but then--
-The more I think about this, actually,

02:43.789 --> 02:47.334
