03:05.060 --> 03:07.396
just because
you did me so good back there.

03:07.479 --> 03:08.689
-[scoffs]
-I don't know.

03:08.772 --> 03:10.649
Do you want to get
some, like, fast food and...

03:10.732 --> 03:13.819
