03:23.161 --> 03:25.497
<i>♪ I'm just a girl in love ♪</i>

03:25.580 --> 03:27.290
<i>♪ La, la, la, lovey dove ♪</i>

03:27.374 --> 03:30.502
<i>♪ I can't be held responsible</i>
<i>for my actions ♪</i>

03:30.585 --> 03:31.628
<i>♪ She's an ingénue ♪</i>

03:31.712 --> 03:33.672
